>}\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"否\"</span>}\n}\n</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n','1. 在el-table-column标签中加入 :formatter=\"formate\"\n2. 在methods中添加方法 formate\n3. 方法如下\n```\nformate(val)\n{\n	if(val==0){return \"是\"}\n	else{return \"否\"}\n}\n```',0,1,1,0,1,'vue2.0的Element UI的表格table把数字格式化为其他内容','vue2.0的Element UI的表格table把数字格式化为其他内容',0,'2018-10-11 10:00:34','2018-10-11 10:00:34'),(34,'ubuntu 同步 ntp',1,'',NULL,1,'<ol>\n<li>安装ntp客户端<code>apt-get install ntpdate</code></li>\n<li>ntpdate ip地址</li>\n</ol>\n','1. 安装ntp客户端`apt-get install ntpdate`\n2. ntpdate ip地址',0,3,1,0,1,'ubuntu 同步 ntp','ubuntu 同步 ntp',0,'2018-10-12 13:11:53','2018-10-12 13:11:53'),(35,'springboot集成swagger',1,'zhyd/cover/20181012132349156.png',NULL,1,'<ol>\n<li>引入依赖<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">springfox-swagger2.version</span>&gt;</span>2.2.2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">springfox-swagger2.version</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>io.springfox<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>springfox-swagger2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>${springfox-swagger2.version}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>io.springfox<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>springfox-swagger-ui<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>${springfox-swagger2.version}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>添加配置类</p>\n<pre><code>     <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Configuration</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@EnableSwagger</span>2\n     <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">SwaggerConfig</span> </span>{\n         <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n          * 可以注入多个doket，也就是多个版本的api，可以在看到有三个版本groupName不能是重复的，v1和v2是ant风格匹配，配置文件\n      * api查看地址:http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html\n      * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return</span>\n      */</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Bean</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> Docket <span class=\"hljs-title\">api</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n         <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//可以添加多个header或参数</span>\n         ParameterBuilder aParameterBuilder = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ParameterBuilder();\n         aParameterBuilder\n                 .parameterType(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"header\"</span>)\n                 .name(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Authorization\"</span>)\n                 .description(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"header中Authorization字段用于认证\"</span>)\n                 .modelRef(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ModelRef(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"string\"</span>))\n                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//非必需，这里是全局配置，然而在登陆的时候是不用验证的</span>\n                 .required(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>).build();\n         List&lt;Parameter&gt; aParameters = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;Parameter&gt;();\n         aParameters.add(aParameterBuilder.build());\n                     <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> Docket(DocumentationType.SWAGGER_2).groupName(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"v1\"</span>).select().apis(RequestHandlerSelectors.basePackage(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"com.weishilvjian.freapi.controller\"</span>))\n                         .paths(PathSelectors.any()).build().apiInfo(apiInfo1()).globalOperationParameters(aParameters);\n         <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//                ;</span>\n             }\n\n         <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> ApiInfo <span class=\"hljs-title\">apiInfo1</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n             <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ApiInfoBuilder()\n                     .title(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"sihuatech  api\"</span>)\n                     .contact(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"wjh\"</span>)\n                     .version(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"v0.01\"</span>)\n                     .build();\n         }\n\n     }\n</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>使用<br> 在controller类上添加注解:<code>@Api(value = &quot;用来提供FRE,FCE以及OCR等接口&quot;)</code><br> 在方法上添加注解(我的参数格式是@RequestBody JSONObject param这样的,其它格式的请参照网上教程):<br> `@ApiOperation(value=&quot;FCE接口&quot;, notes=&quot;json格式参数&quot;,produces = &quot;application/json&quot;)<br> @ApiImplicitParams({</p>\n<pre><code>     @<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">ApiImplicitParam</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">name</span>=\"<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">param</span>\",<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">value</span>= <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"{\\\"mobile\\\":\\\"17765071662\\\",\\\"passWord\\\":\\\"123456\\\"}\"</span>,dataType=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"string\"</span>, paramType = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"body\"</span>)})`\n</code></pre></li>\n<li>效果如下图:<br><img src=\"http://pdlmj6kjo.bkt.clouddn.com/2018-10-12_131907.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ol>\n','1. 引入依赖\n```\n<springfox-swagger2.version>2.2.2</springfox-swagger2.version>\n<dependency>\n            <groupId>io.springfox</groupId>\n            <artifactId>springfox-swagger2</artifactId>\n            <version>${springfox-swagger2.version}</version>\n        </dependency>\n        <dependency>\n            <groupId>io.springfox</groupId>\n            <artifactId>springfox-swagger-ui</artifactId>\n            <version>${springfox-swagger2.version}</version>\n        </dependency>\n```\n2. 添加配置类\n```\n		@Configuration\n		@EnableSwagger2\n		public class SwaggerConfig {\n			/**\n			 * 可以注入多个doket，也就是多个版本的api，可以在看到有三个版本groupName不能是重复的，v1和v2是ant风格匹配，配置文件\n		 * api查看地址:http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html\n		 * @return\n		 */\n		@Bean\n		public Docket api() {\n			//可以添加多个header或参数\n			ParameterBuilder aParameterBuilder = new ParameterBuilder();\n			aParameterBuilder\n					.parameterType(\"header\")\n					.name(\"Authorization\")\n					.description(\"header中Authorization字段用于认证\")\n					.modelRef(new ModelRef(\"string\"))\n					//非必需，这里是全局配置，然而在登陆的时候是不用验证的\n					.required(false).build();\n			List<Parameter> aParameters = new ArrayList<Parameter>();\n			aParameters.add(aParameterBuilder.build());\n						return new Docket(DocumentationType.SWAGGER_2).groupName(\"v1\").select().apis(RequestHandlerSelectors.basePackage(\"com.weishilvjian.freapi.controller\"))\n							.paths(PathSelectors.any()).build().apiInfo(apiInfo1()).globalOperationParameters(aParameters);\n			//                ;\n				}\n\n			private ApiInfo apiInfo1() {\n				return new ApiInfoBuilder()\n						.title(\"sihuatech  api\")\n						.contact(\"wjh\")\n						.version(\"v0.01\")\n						.build();\n			}\n\n		}\n```\n\n3. 使用\n	在controller类上添加注解:`@Api(value = \"用来提供FRE,FCE以及OCR等接口\")`\n	在方法上添加注解(我的参数格式是@RequestBody JSONObject param这样的,其它格式的请参照网上教程):\n	`@ApiOperation(value=\"FCE接口\", notes=\"json格式参数\",produces = \"application/json\")\n    @ApiImplicitParams({\n            @ApiImplicitParam(name=\"param\",value= \"{\\\"mobile\\\":\\\"17765071662\\\",\\\"passWord\\\":\\\"123456\\\"}\",dataType=\"string\", paramType = \"body\")})`\n4. 效果如下图:\n![](http://pdlmj6kjo.bkt.clouddn.com/2018-10-12_131907.png)',0,2,1,0,1,'springboot集成swagger','springboot集成swagger',0,'2018-10-12 13:23:49','2018-10-12 13:23:49'),(36,' Java泛型中<？ extends E>和<？ super E>的区别',1,'zhyd/cover/20181018173405703.jpg',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/asdfsadfasdfsa/article/details/52794573?utm_source=blogxgwz4\">https://blog.csdn.net/asdfsadfasdfsa/article/details/52794573?utm_source=blogxgwz4</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/asdfsadfasdfsa/article/details/52794573?utm_source=blogxgwz4',0,2,1,0,0,'Java泛型中<？ extends E>和<？ super E>的区别','Java泛型中<？ extends E>和<？ super E>的区别',0,'2018-10-18 17:34:06','2018-10-18 17:34:06'),(37,'定时将ubuntu上的mysql数据库备份到github',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://icharle.com/Linuxbak.html\">https://icharle.com/Linuxbak.html</a></p>\n','https://icharle.com/Linuxbak.html',0,3,1,0,0,'定时将ubuntu上的mysql数据库备份到github','定时将ubuntu上的mysql数据库备份到github',0,'2018-10-18 18:45:31','2018-10-18 18:45:31'),(38,'maven引入本地jar包',1,'',NULL,1,'<p>1.先将jar包安装到本地仓库<br>mvn install:install-file -Dfile=jar包的位置 -DgroupId=上面的groupId -DartifactId=上面的artifactId -Dversion=上面的version -Dpackaging=jar </p>\n<ol>\n<li>在pom文件中添加依赖就可以了,跟安装到本地仓库的版本要一致.</li>\n</ol>\n','1.先将jar包安装到本地仓库\nmvn install:install-file -Dfile=jar包的位置 -DgroupId=上面的groupId -DartifactId=上面的artifactId -Dversion=上面的version -Dpackaging=jar \n2. 在pom文件中添加依赖就可以了,跟安装到本地仓库的版本要一致.',0,2,1,0,0,'maven引入本地jar包','maven引入本地jar包',0,'2018-10-24 11:42:17','2018-10-24 20:38:17'),(39,'docker基础容器中安装java',1,'',NULL,1,'<ol>\n<li>下载对应系统的java版本到宿主机<br><a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html\">http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html</a></li>\n<li>进入容器<br>docker exec -it &lt;容器名称或者ID&gt; bash</li>\n<li>将java压缩包从宿主机拷贝到容器指定目录<br>docker cp java路径 容器名称:容器中的路径</li>\n<li>解压<br>tar -zxvf  jdk-8u121-linux-x64.tar.gz</li>\n<li>创建java目录<br>mkdir /usr/lib/java</li>\n<li>将解压后的java剪切到该目录<br>cp 源文件路径  目标文件路径</li>\n<li>设置环境变量 vim ~/.bashrc<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/java/jdk1.8.0_121\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> JRE_HOME=<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JAVA_HOME}</span>/jre  \n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> CLASSPATH=.:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JAVA_HOME}</span>/lib:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JRE_HOME}</span>/lib  \n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> PATH=<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JAVA_HOME}</span>/bin:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$PATH</span>\n</code></pre></li>\n<li>刷新环境变量<br>source ~/.bashrc</li>\n<li>验证<br>java -version</li>\n</ol>\n','1. 下载对应系统的java版本到宿主机\nhttp://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html\n2. 进入容器\ndocker exec -it <容器名称或者ID> bash\n3. 将java压缩包从宿主机拷贝到容器指定目录\ndocker cp java路径 容器名称:容器中的路径\n4. 解压\ntar -zxvf  jdk-8u121-linux-x64.tar.gz\n5. 创建java目录\nmkdir /usr/lib/java\n6. 将解压后的java剪切到该目录\ncp 源文件路径  目标文件路径\n7. 设置环境变量 vim ~/.bashrc\n```\nexport JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/java/jdk1.8.0_121\nexport JRE_HOME=${JAVA_HOME}/jre  \nexport CLASSPATH=.:${JAVA_HOME}/lib:${JRE_HOME}/lib  \nexport PATH=${JAVA_HOME}/bin:$PATH \n```\n8. 刷新环境变量\nsource ~/.bashrc\n9. 验证\njava -version',0,6,1,0,1,'docker基础容器中安装java','docker基础容器中安装java',1,'2018-10-25 17:46:34','2018-10-25 17:46:34'),(40,'使用docker官方的mysql镜像',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/nzyalj/article/details/79177291\">https://blog.csdn.net/nzyalj/article/details/79177291</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/nzyalj/article/details/79177291',0,3,1,0,0,'使用docker官方的mysql镜像','使用docker官方的mysql镜像',0,'2018-10-25 17:49:38','2018-10-25 17:49:38'),(41,'java中使用BASE64编码图片 然后再解码保存',1,'',NULL,1,'<pre><code> String str = Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(Files.readAllBytes(Paths.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">get</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\Desktop\\\\TrafficFlowTest.jpg\"</span>)));\n  Files.write(Paths.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">get</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\Desktop\\\\b.jpg\"</span>), Base64.getDecoder().decode(str), StandardOpenOption.CREATE);\n</code></pre>','```\n String str = Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(Files.readAllBytes(Paths.get(\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\Desktop\\\\TrafficFlowTest.jpg\")));\n  Files.write(Paths.get(\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\Desktop\\\\b.jpg\"), Base64.getDecoder().decode(str), StandardOpenOption.CREATE);\n\n```',0,2,1,0,1,'java中使用BASE64编码图片 然后再解码保存','java BASE64编码图片 ',1,'2018-11-06 18:52:44','2018-11-06 18:52:44'),(42,'vue中使用el-date-picker 设置默认值',1,'zhyd/cover/20181010190837047.jpg',NULL,1,'<p>date-picker获取的时间传到后台不能被正常解析,所以使用<br>format=&quot;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss&quot;<br>value-format=&quot;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss&quot;<br>以及getSTime这个方法把日期给格式化,后台就能正常接收了</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;el-date-picker\n          v-model=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"query.begainTime\"</span>\n          type=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"datetime\"</span>\n          format=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"</span>\n          value-format=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"</span>\n          placeholder=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"选择起始日期\"</span>\n          align=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"left\"</span>\n          @change=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"getSTime\"</span>\n          <span class=\"hljs-symbol\">:picker-options=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"pickerOptions\"</span>&gt;</span>\n        &lt;<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">/el-date-picker&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><p>在data中添加如下对象:</p>\n<pre><code>pickerOptions: {\n          <span class=\"hljs-attr\">shortcuts</span>: [{\n            <span class=\"hljs-attr\">text</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'一周前\'</span>,\n            onClick(picker) {\n              <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> date = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>();\n              date.setTime(date.getTime() - <span class=\"hljs-number\">3600</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">24</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>);\n              picker.$emit(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'pick\'</span>, date);\n            }\n          }, {\n            <span class=\"hljs-attr\">text</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'昨天\'</span>,\n            onClick(picker) {\n              <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> date = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>();\n              date.setTime(date.getTime() - <span class=\"hljs-number\">3600</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">24</span>);\n              picker.$emit(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'pick\'</span>, date);\n            }\n          }, {\n            <span class=\"hljs-attr\">text</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'今天零点\'</span>,\n            onClick(picker) {\n                <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//获取当天零点</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> date = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>().toLocaleDateString()).getTime());\n              <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//获取当天晚上24点</span>\n              <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//const start = new Date(new Date(new Date().toLocaleDateString()).getTime()+24*60*60*1000-1);</span>\n              picker.$emit(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'pick\'</span>,date);\n            }\n          },{\n            <span class=\"hljs-attr\">text</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'一小时前\'</span>,\n            onClick(picker) {\n              <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> date = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>();\n              date.setTime(date.getTime() - <span class=\"hljs-number\">3600</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span> * <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>);\n              picker.$emit(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'pick\'</span>, date);\n            }\n          },{\n            <span class=\"hljs-attr\">text</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'当前时间\'</span>,\n            onClick(picker) {\n              picker.$emit(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'pick\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>());\n            }\n          }]\n        },\n</code></pre><p>加入如下的方法:</p>\n<pre><code> getSTime(val) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.query.begainTime=val;<span class=\"hljs-comment\">//这个sTime是在data中声明的，也就是v-model绑定的值</span>\n      },\n</code></pre><p>效果如下<br><img src=\"http://pdlmj6kjo.bkt.clouddn.com/20181114180740.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n','date-picker获取的时间传到后台不能被正常解析,所以使用\nformat=\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\nvalue-format=\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n以及getSTime这个方法把日期给格式化,后台就能正常接收了\n```\n<el-date-picker\n          v-model=\"query.begainTime\"\n          type=\"datetime\"\n          format=\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n          value-format=\"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n          placeholder=\"选择起始日期\"\n          align=\"left\"\n          @change=\"getSTime\"\n          :picker-options=\"pickerOptions\">\n        </el-date-picker>\n```\n在data中添加如下对象:\n```\npickerOptions: {\n          shortcuts: [{\n            text: \'一周前\',\n            onClick(picker) {\n              const date = new Date();\n              date.setTime(date.getTime() - 3600 * 1000 * 24 * 7);\n              picker.$emit(\'pick\', date);\n            }\n          }, {\n            text: \'昨天\',\n            onClick(picker) {\n              const date = new Date();\n              date.setTime(date.getTime() - 3600 * 1000 * 24);\n              picker.$emit(\'pick\', date);\n            }\n          }, {\n            text: \'今天零点\',\n            onClick(picker) {\n				//获取当天零点\n              const date = new Date(new Date(new Date().toLocaleDateString()).getTime());\n			  //获取当天晚上24点\n			  //const start = new Date(new Date(new Date().toLocaleDateString()).getTime()+24*60*60*1000-1);\n              picker.$emit(\'pick\',date);\n            }\n          },{\n            text: \'一小时前\',\n            onClick(picker) {\n              const date = new Date();\n              date.setTime(date.getTime() - 3600 * 1000 * 1);\n              picker.$emit(\'pick\', date);\n            }\n          },{\n            text: \'当前时间\',\n            onClick(picker) {\n              picker.$emit(\'pick\', new Date());\n            }\n          }]\n        },\n```\n加入如下的方法:\n```\n getSTime(val) {\n        this.query.begainTime=val;//这个sTime是在data中声明的，也就是v-model绑定的值\n      },\n```\n效果如下\n![](http://pdlmj6kjo.bkt.clouddn.com/20181114180740.png)',0,1,1,0,1,'vue中使用el-date-picker 设置默认值','vue中使用el-date-picker 设置默认值',1,'2018-11-14 18:09:04','2018-11-14 18:09:04'),(43,'Linux常用指令',1,'zhyd/cover/20181119161818805.jpg',NULL,1,'<p>更新中...</p>\n<ol>\n<li>解压缩<br> 将文件压缩为tgz格式:<pre><code> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">tar</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">-zcvf</span>  目标文件名<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.tgz</span> 源文件\n</code></pre></li>\n<li>shell脚本创建定时任务,<br> 首先安装apt install crontab,$1表示执行脚本时的第一个参数,sed命令中如果要使用变量,需要用三个单引号包起来.<br> 首先删除指定的行,然后用sed命令追加一行到文件末<pre><code> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#!/bin/bash</span>\n sed -i <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'14d\'</span> /etc/crontab\n sed -i <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'$a */\'</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\'\'</span>$<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\'\'\' *    * * *   root   ntpdate \'\'\'</span>$<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\'\'\'\' /etc/crontab</span>\n</code></pre> -------------------------2019年1月15更新-----------------------------------</li>\n<li>scp将文件/文件夹从本地拷至远程服务器<br>  scp -r test.txt username@remote_ip:/opt/</li>\n<li>scp将文件/文件夹从远程服务器拷至本地<br>  scp -r username@remote_ip:/opt/test.txt /opt/</li>\n</ol>\n','更新中...\n1. 解压缩\n	将文件压缩为tgz格式:\n	```\n	tar -zcvf  目标文件名.tgz 源文件\n	```\n2. shell脚本创建定时任务,\n	首先安装apt install crontab,$1表示执行脚本时的第一个参数,sed命令中如果要使用变量,需要用三个单引号包起来.\n	首先删除指定的行,然后用sed命令追加一行到文件末\n	```\n	#!/bin/bash\n	sed -i \'14d\' /etc/crontab\n	sed -i \'$a */\'\'\'$1\'\'\' *    * * *   root   ntpdate \'\'\'$2\'\'\'\' /etc/crontab\n	```\n	-------------------------2019年1月15更新-----------------------------------\n3. scp将文件/文件夹从本地拷至远程服务器\n	 scp -r test.txt username@remote_ip:/opt/\n4. scp将文件/文件夹从远程服务器拷至本地\n	 scp -r username@remote_ip:/opt/test.txt /opt/\n\n\n',0,2,1,0,1,'Linux常用命令','Linux常用命令',1,'2018-11-19 16:18:19','2019-01-15 18:07:15'),(44,'mysql常用命令',1,'zhyd/cover/20181119162041102.jpg',NULL,1,'<p>持续更新中...</p>\n<ol>\n<li>查看MySql数据库物理文件存放位置<br> show global variables like &quot;%datadir%&quot;;</li>\n</ol>\n','持续更新中...\n1. 查看MySql数据库物理文件存放位置\n	show global variables like \"%datadir%\";',0,2,1,0,1,'mysql常用命令','mysql常用命令',1,'2018-11-19 16:20:41','2018-11-19 16:20:41'),(45,'docker常用命令',1,'zhyd/cover/20181119163046020.jpg',NULL,1,'<ul>\n<li><ol>\n<li>创建并运行一个容器<br>-d表示后台运行 --network=host表示容器内部的所有端口映射为宿主机的端口  -v表示挂载到宿主机的位置<br><code>docker run -d --network=host -v /data/mysql:/var/lib/mysql -v /data:/data  --name=jserver --restart=always 容器名</code></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><ol>\n<li>把一个容器提交为一个镜像<br>冒号后面为标签<br><code>docker commit -m &#39;XXX&#39; -a &#39;XXX&#39; 镜像id  名称:20181119</code></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><ol>\n<li>把一个镜像导出到文件<br>docker sava 镜像id &gt; 文件名.tar</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n','* 1. 创建并运行一个容器\n	-d表示后台运行 --network=host表示容器内部的所有端口映射为宿主机的端口  -v表示挂载到宿主机的位置\n	`docker run -d --network=host -v /data/mysql:/var/lib/mysql -v /data:/data  --name=jserver --restart=always 容器名`\n	\n* 2. 把一个容器提交为一个镜像\n	冒号后面为标签 \n	`docker commit -m \'XXX\' -a \'XXX\' 镜像id  名称:20181119`\n	\n* 3. 把一个镜像导出到文件\n	docker sava 镜像id > 文件名.tar',0,6,1,0,1,'docker常用命令','docker常用命令',1,'2018-11-19 16:30:47','2018-11-19 16:31:51'),(46,'java中重写toString方法为json格式',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/zipon/p/6208346.html\">https://www.cnblogs.com/zipon/p/6208346.html</a></p>\n','https://www.cnblogs.com/zipon/p/6208346.html',0,3,1,0,0,'java中重写toString方法为json格式','java中重写toString方法为json格式',0,'2018-11-30 11:37:19','2018-11-30 11:37:19'),(47,'vue中使用vue2-highcharts遇到的一些问题',1,'',NULL,1,'<p>如果坐标轴是时间轴,那么series的格式应为:</p>\n<pre><code>series: [\n            {name: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'名称\'</span>,\n              data: [], \n            }\n          ],\n</code></pre><p>data的格式为(x对应横坐标的值,y对应纵坐标的值):</p>\n<pre><code>[[x,y],[x,y],[x,y]......]\n</code></pre><p>横坐标如果是时间的话,那么x的取值类型是Number的,也就是说要获取时间戳,获取时间戳的代码如下:</p>\n<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> someDate = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"日期字符串,格式为:yyyy-mm-dd HH:mm:ss\"</span>)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> x = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>.UTC(someDate.getFullYear(), someDate.getMonth(), someDate.getDate(), someDate.getHours(), someDate.getMinutes(), someDate.getSeconds());\n</code></pre><p>从后台取的数据日期格式要重写格式化成UTC的,并添加到相应的series的data中,代码如下(data.data是后台返回的数组,,数组格式也是[[x,y],[x,y],[x,y]......]这个格式):</p>\n<pre><code>vm.$refs.lineCharts.getChart().series[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>].setData(data.data.map(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">v</span> =&gt;</span> {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> someDate =<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>(v[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>])\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> tms = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Date</span>.UTC(someDate.getFullYear(), someDate.getMonth(), someDate.getDate(), someDate.getHours(),someDate.getMinutes(),someDate.getSeconds());\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span>[tms,v[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]]\n          }))\n</code></pre><p>因为我的折线图是动态加载的,使用的websocket,当后台有数据的时候就传到前台,折线图重新绘制一个点(如果第三个参数为false则新加一个点时不会挤掉最开始的那个点,这样做的意义是初始的数据以及后来动态加载的数据都会显示在折线图上,而不会每次增加一个点最开始的点就被删除):</p>\n<pre><code>this.<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$refs</span>.lineCharts.getChart().series[0].addPoint([x, y], <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>);\n</code></pre>','如果坐标轴是时间轴,那么series的格式应为:\n```\nseries: [\n            {name: \'名称\',\n              data: [], \n            }\n          ],\n```\ndata的格式为(x对应横坐标的值,y对应纵坐标的值):\n```\n[[x,y],[x,y],[x,y]......]\n```\n横坐标如果是时间的话,那么x的取值类型是Number的,也就是说要获取时间戳,获取时间戳的代码如下:\n```\nvar someDate = new Date(\"日期字符串,格式为:yyyy-mm-dd HH:mm:ss\")\n        var x = Date.UTC(someDate.getFullYear(), someDate.getMonth(), someDate.getDate(), someDate.getHours(), someDate.getMinutes(), someDate.getSeconds());\n```\n\n从后台取的数据日期格式要重写格式化成UTC的,并添加到相应的series的data中,代码如下(data.data是后台返回的数组,,数组格式也是[[x,y],[x,y],[x,y]......]这个格式):\n```\nvm.$refs.lineCharts.getChart().series[0].setData(data.data.map(v => {\n            var someDate =new Date(v[0])\n            var tms = Date.UTC(someDate.getFullYear(), someDate.getMonth(), someDate.getDate(), someDate.getHours(),someDate.getMinutes(),someDate.getSeconds());\n            return[tms,v[1]]\n          }))\n```\n\n因为我的折线图是动态加载的,使用的websocket,当后台有数据的时候就传到前台,折线图重新绘制一个点(如果第三个参数为false则新加一个点时不会挤掉最开始的那个点,这样做的意义是初始的数据以及后来动态加载的数据都会显示在折线图上,而不会每次增加一个点最开始的点就被删除):\n```\nthis.$refs.lineCharts.getChart().series[0].addPoint([x, y], true, false);\n```',0,1,1,0,1,'vue中使用vue2-highcharts遇到的一些问题','vue中使用vue2-highcharts遇到的一些问题',1,'2018-11-30 12:00:41','2018-11-30 12:00:41'),(48,'fastjson格式化java对象为json字符串',1,'',NULL,1,'<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">String</span> data = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">JSON</span>.toJSONString(java对象, SerializerFeature.DisableCircularReferenceDetect,SerializerFeature.WriteDateUseDateFormat);\n</code></pre>','```\nString data = JSON.toJSONString(java对象, SerializerFeature.DisableCircularReferenceDetect,SerializerFeature.WriteDateUseDateFormat);\n```',0,2,1,0,1,'fastjson格式化java对象为json字符串','fastjson格式化java对象为json字符串',0,'2018-11-30 12:03:35','2018-11-30 12:03:35'),(49,'ubuntu开启root用户',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/sunxiaoju/article/details/51993091\">https://blog.csdn.net/sunxiaoju/article/details/51993091</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/sunxiaoju/article/details/51993091',0,3,1,0,0,'ubuntu开启root用户','ubuntu开启root用户',0,'2018-12-05 13:22:19','2018-12-05 13:22:19'),(50,'ubuntu安装nvidia驱动',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ghw15221836342/article/details/79571559\">https://blog.csdn.net/ghw15221836342/article/details/79571559</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/ghw15221836342/article/details/79571559',0,3,1,0,0,'ubuntu安装nvidia驱动','ubuntu安装nvidia驱动',0,'2018-12-05 13:25:09','2018-12-05 13:25:09'),(51,'java中求百分比',1,'zhyd/cover/20181212095638664.jpg',NULL,1,'<p>第一种方式：</p>\n<pre><code>NumberFormat nf = NumberFormat.getPercentInstance();\nnf.setMinimumFractionDigits(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);<span class=\"hljs-comment\">//控制保留小数点后几位，2：表示保留2位小数点</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">String</span> percent = nf.format(浮点数如：<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.2398</span>);\n</code></pre><p>第二种方式：</p>\n<pre><code>DecimalFormat df1 = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DecimalFormat(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"0.00%\"</span>);    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//##.00%   百分比格式，后面不足2位的用0补齐  </span>\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">String</span> result= df1.format(浮点数);\n</code></pre>','第一种方式：\n```\nNumberFormat nf = NumberFormat.getPercentInstance();\nnf.setMinimumFractionDigits(2);//控制保留小数点后几位，2：表示保留2位小数点\nString percent = nf.format(浮点数如：0.2398);\n```\n第二种方式：\n```\nDecimalFormat df1 = new DecimalFormat(\"0.00%\");    //##.00%   百分比格式，后面不足2位的用0补齐  \nString result= df1.format(浮点数);  \n```',0,2,1,0,1,'java中求百分比','java中求百分比',0,'2018-12-12 09:56:40','2018-12-12 09:56:40'),(52,'vue中setInterval 使用',1,'zhyd/cover/20181010190837047.jpg',NULL,1,'<p>vue 是单页面应用，路由切换后，定时器并不会自动关闭，需要手动清除，当页面被销毁时，清除定时器即可</p>\n<pre><code>mounted() {\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> vm = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>\n      vm.interval = setInterval(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) </span>{\n        vm.indexCard();\n      }, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3000</span>);\n    },\n    destroyed(){\n      clearInterval(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.interval)\n    },\n</code></pre>','vue 是单页面应用，路由切换后，定时器并不会自动关闭，需要手动清除，当页面被销毁时，清除定时器即可\n```\nmounted() {\n      let vm = this\n      vm.interval = setInterval(function () {\n        vm.indexCard();\n      }, 3000);\n    },\n    destroyed(){\n      clearInterval(this.interval)\n    },\n```',0,1,1,0,1,'vue中setInterval 使用','vue中setInterval 使用',1,'2018-12-18 11:33:39','2018-12-18 11:33:39'),(53,'cuda ImportError: libcudart.so.7.0: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory',1,'zhyd/cover/20181018173405703.jpg',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/4a9d7c0d44ad\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/4a9d7c0d44ad</a></p>\n<pre><code>sudo ldconfig /usr/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">local</span>/cuda/lib64\n</code></pre>','https://www.jianshu.com/p/4a9d7c0d44ad\n```\nsudo ldconfig /usr/local/cuda/lib64\n```',0,3,1,0,0,'ImportError: libcudart.so.7.0: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory','ImportError: libcudart.so.7.0: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory',0,'2018-12-24 17:11:52','2018-12-24 17:11:52'),(54,'cudnn7.1 安装cuDNN 7.1',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/DarrenXf/article/details/82182449\">https://blog.csdn.net/DarrenXf/article/details/82182449</a></p>\n<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> tar -zxvf cudnn-9.2-linux-x64-v7.1.tgz</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> sudo cp cuda/include/cudnn.h /usr/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">local</span>/cuda/include/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> sudo cp cuda/lib64/libcudnn* /usr/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">local</span>/cuda/lib64/ -d </span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> sudo chmod a+r /usr/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">local</span>/cuda/include/cudnn.h</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> sudo chmod a+r /usr/<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">local</span>/cuda/lib64/libcudnn*</span>\n</code></pre>','https://blog.csdn.net/DarrenXf/article/details/82182449\n\n```\n$ tar -zxvf cudnn-9.2-linux-x64-v7.1.tgz\n$ sudo cp cuda/include/cudnn.h /usr/local/cuda/include/\n$ sudo cp cuda/lib64/libcudnn* /usr/local/cuda/lib64/ -d \n$ sudo chmod a+r /usr/local/cuda/include/cudnn.h\n$ sudo chmod a+r /usr/local/cuda/lib64/libcudnn*\n```',0,3,1,0,0,'cudnn7.1 安装cuDNN 7.1','cudnn7.1 安装cuDNN 7.1',0,'2018-12-24 17:13:26','2018-12-24 17:13:26'),(55,'ubuntu禁止内核更新（更新内核后显卡驱动也要重新安装，很烦人）',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/medsci/p/8338170.html\">https://www.cnblogs.com/medsci/p/8338170.html</a></p>\n<pre><code>查看内核列表\ndpkg --<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">get</span>-selections |grep linux-image\n查看正在使用的内核\nuname -a\n移除旧的内核\nsudo apt-<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">get</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">remove</span> linux-image<span class=\"hljs-number\">-4.10</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">-28</span>-generic\nsudo apt-<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">get</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">remove</span> linux-image-extra<span class=\"hljs-number\">-4.10</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">-28</span>-generic \n禁止更新内核\nsudo apt-mark hold linux-image<span class=\"hljs-number\">-4.13</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">-31</span>-generic\n</code></pre>','https://www.cnblogs.com/medsci/p/8338170.html\n\n```\n查看内核列表\ndpkg --get-selections |grep linux-image\n查看正在使用的内核\nuname -a\n移除旧的内核\nsudo apt-get remove linux-image-4.10.0-28-generic\nsudo apt-get remove linux-image-extra-4.10.0-28-generic \n禁止更新内核\nsudo apt-mark hold linux-image-4.13.0-31-generic\n```',0,3,1,0,0,'ubuntu禁止内核更新','ubuntu禁止内核更新',0,'2018-12-24 18:23:09','2018-12-24 18:23:09'),(56,'ubuntu安装搜狗输入法',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/areigninhell/article/details/79696751\">https://blog.csdn.net/areigninhell/article/details/79696751</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/areigninhell/article/details/79696751',0,3,1,0,0,'ubuntu安装搜狗输入法','ubuntu安装搜狗输入法',0,'2018-12-24 18:23:44','2018-12-24 18:23:44'),(57,'vue中清除定时器',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_21132509/article/details/83504522\">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_21132509/article/details/83504522</a><br>方式一：</p>\n<pre><code>beforeDestroy() {\n    clearInterval(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.timer);        \n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.timer = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>;\n}\n</code></pre><p>方式二：</p>\n<pre><code>const timer = setInterval(<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> =&gt;</span>{                    \n    <span class=\"hljs-regexp\">//</span> 某些定时器操作                \n}, <span class=\"hljs-number\">500</span>);            \n<span class=\"hljs-regexp\">//</span> 通过$once来监听定时器，在beforeDestroy钩子可以被清除。\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.$once(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'hook:beforeDestroy\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> =&gt;</span> {            \n    clearInterval(timer);                                    \n})\n</code></pre>','https://blog.csdn.net/qq_21132509/article/details/83504522\n方式一：\n\n```\nbeforeDestroy() {\n    clearInterval(this.timer);        \n    this.timer = null;\n}\n```\n方式二：\n```\nconst timer = setInterval(() =>{                    \n    // 某些定时器操作                \n}, 500);            \n// 通过$once来监听定时器，在beforeDestroy钩子可以被清除。\nthis.$once(\'hook:beforeDestroy\', () => {            \n    clearInterval(timer);                                    \n})\n```',0,1,1,0,0,'vue中清除定时器','vue中清除定时器',0,'2018-12-28 18:12:21','2018-12-28 18:12:21'),(59,'IDEA项目左边栏只能看到文件看不到项目结构',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42362985/article/details/80538064\">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42362985/article/details/80538064</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42362985/article/details/80538064',0,3,1,0,0,'IDEA项目左边栏只能看到文件看不到项目结构','IDEA项目左边栏只能看到文件看不到项目结构',0,'2019-01-09 14:58:26','2019-01-09 14:58:26'),(60,'maven使用阿里云中央仓库',1,'',NULL,1,'<p>在maven的安装目录下修改conf/setting.xml文件</p>\n<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">mirrors</span>&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">mirror</span>&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">id</span>&gt;</span>alimaven<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">id</span>&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">name</span>&gt;</span>aliyun maven<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">name</span>&gt;</span>\n  　　<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>http://maven.aliyun.com/nexus/content/groups/public/<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">url</span>&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span>central<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span>        \n    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">mirror</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">mirrors</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre>','在maven的安装目录下修改conf/setting